Bucket list moment at Giraffe Manor in Nairobi, Kenya 🇰🇪 Wanna see your content posted in our account? Get a feature visiting viewfervor.com (link in our bio: @viewfervor)

Have you ever been this close to a giraffe in person before? 🦒

📽 @venelin_k & @inagallardo_adamand
📍 Giraffe Manor, Nairobi, Kenya
🎶 Jerusalema - Master KG Feat. Nomcebo Zikode

This is Indonesia🇮🇩 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting viewfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @viewfervor

Which spot is your favorite from 1 - 10?😍

Locations and Videos:
1. Rumah Pohon @lifewithelliott
2. Uluwatu @earthbestshots
3. Kuningan @heru_montana
4. Diamond Beach @naturebeauty8967
5. Bali @lucymoonstone
6. Nusa Penida @doounias
7. Raja Ampat @travisburkephotography
8. The Edge Bali @thiago.lopez
9. LekeLeke Waterfall @zhilistii
10. Sumba @agirlwhoblooms
